## 1. Functional Test Cases — Happy Path

### TC-001: injectAll — Copy all components with valid language

|  |  |
| --- | --- |
| Field | Value |
| **ID** | TC-001 |
| **Level** | UT-01 |
| **Priority** | High |
| **Type** | Functional |
| **Requirement** | UC-1, BR-1, BR-2, Story 1 |
| **Preconditions** | Extension installed; workspace open; resources/agents, resources/steering, resources/hooks, resources/templates, resources/scripts/python all exist |

**Test Steps:**

|  |  |  |
| --- | --- | --- |
| Step | Action | Expected Result |
| 1 | Call injectAll(“python”) with valid extensionPath and workspaceRoot | Function executes without error |
| 2 | Verify .kiro/agents exists in workspace | Directory exists with all files from resources/agents |
| 3 | Verify .kiro/steering exists in workspace | Directory exists with all files from resources/steering |
| 4 | Verify .kiro/hooks exists in workspace | Directory exists with all files from resources/hooks |
| 5 | Verify documents/templates exists in workspace | Directory exists with all files from resources/templates |
| 6 | Verify .analysis/code-intelligence/scripts/python exists | Only python indexer scripts copied |

**Test Data:** indexerLanguage = “python”, extensionPath = “/mock/ext”, workspaceRoot = “/mock/ws” **Postconditions:** All 4 CORE\_COMPONENTS + python indexer exist in workspace

### TC-002: injectSelective — Select and inject specific components

|  |  |
| --- | --- |
| Field | Value |
