### TC-100: injectAll — One component source directory missing (AF-1)

|  |  |
| --- | --- |
| Field | Value |
| **ID** | TC-100 |
| **Level** | UT-06 |
| **Priority** | High |
| **Type** | Functional — Alternative Flow |
| **Requirement** | UC-1 AF-1, BR-7 |
| **Preconditions** | Extension resources missing resources/steering directory; other 3 components exist |

**Test Steps:**

|  |  |  |
| --- | --- | --- |
| Step | Action | Expected Result |
| 1 | Call injectAll(“python”) | Function completes (does not throw) |
| 2 | Verify .kiro/agents exists | Copied successfully |
| 3 | Verify .kiro/steering does NOT exist | Skipped (source missing) |
| 4 | Verify .kiro/hooks exists | Copied successfully |
| 5 | Verify documents/templates exists | Copied successfully |
| 6 | Verify warning logged for steering | Log contains “Component ‘steering’ source not found. Skipping.” |

**Test Data:** resources/steering directory removed from extension path **Postconditions:** 3 of 4 components injected; partial success reported

