**Test Steps:**

|  |  |  |
| --- | --- | --- |
| Step | Action | Expected Result |
| 1 | Set destination parent to read-only permissions | Permission denied on write |
| 2 | Call copyDirRecursive(source, destination) | Function throws error |
| 3 | Verify error message mentions permissions | “Cannot write to workspace. Check file permissions.” |

**Test Data:** Destination parent chmod 444 (read-only) **Postconditions:** Error thrown; source unchanged

