| 4 | Select “Python” as indexer language | Injection starts |
| 5 | Wait for completion notification | Success message shown |
| 6 | Open Explorer panel | .kiro/ and documents/ folders visible |
| 7 | Expand .kiro/agents | Agent files present |
| 8 | Expand .kiro/steering | Steering files present |
| 9 | Expand .kiro/hooks | Hook files present |
| 10 | Expand documents/templates | Template files present |
| 11 | Expand .analysis/code-intelligence/scripts/python | Python indexer scripts present |
| 12 | Verify no node\_modules, **pycache**, .git, out, dist in any copied tree | Excluded dirs absent |

**Postconditions:** Full workspace setup complete

