### Environment Configuration

* **Node.js:** v18.x or later (LTS)
* **VS Code:** v1.85 or later
* **Test Framework:** vitest v1.x
* **Mock FS:** mock-fs v5.x (for unit tests)
* **Property Testing:** fast-check v3.x
* **VS Code Test:** @vscode/test-electron v2.x

### Test Execution Commands

# Run all unit tests
npx vitest run --reporter=verbose

# Run property-based tests
npx vitest run --reporter=verbose tests/properties/

# Run integration tests (real file system)
npx vitest run --reporter=verbose tests/integration/

# Run E2E tests (VS Code instance)
npx vscode-test

# Generate coverage report
npx vitest run --coverage